  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  No trauma

          -  Not pregnant

          -  No other cause for seizure (hypoglycemia, CNS causes, trauma)

          -  Good family support

          -  Working telephone contact

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Renal failure (creatine &gt; 2mg/dl

          -  Fever or illness

          -  Hypotension

          -  Any trauma
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
